# Resource hpegl_vmaas_load_balancer_profile

-> Compatible version >= 5.4.6

{{ .Description | trimspace }}
`hpegl_vmaas_load_balancer_profile` resource supports NSX-T Load balancer Profile creation.

For creating an NSX-T Load balancer Profile, use the following examples.

-> NSX-T Profile having HTTP,UDP,TCP,COOKIE,SOURCEIP,GENERIC,SERVER,CLIENT  considered as different Profile types. You can create either HTTP,HTTPS,ICMP,Passive,TCP,UDP, but not everything at the same time.

-> Load Balancer ID Data Source `hpegl_vmaas_load_balancer` is supported for Creating Profile.

